# Hermes Agent (this repo)

- Upstream: [NousResearch/hermes-agent](https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent). Prefer forks + PRs for upstream changes.
- Runtime state lives in `~/.hermes/` (never commit `.env`, `config.yaml` with secrets, or session DBs).
- Dev install: editable `uv pip install -e ".[all,dev]"` in repo `venv/`; local CLI alias `hermes-dev` avoids clashing with production `hermes`.
- Production on Hostinger: deploy via `deploy/hostinger/sync.sh` or `git pull` on VPS + `uv pip install -e ".[all]"` + restart gateway.
- Server facts: read `deploy/hostinger/.server-context.md` if present (regenerate with `./deploy/hostinger/collect-context.sh` after configuring `deploy/hostinger/hostinger.env`).
- New capabilities: prefer **skills** over new **tools** unless integration requires harness code (see CONTRIBUTING.md).
- After Python dep changes, bump pins in `pyproject.toml` and run `uv lock` per project policy.
